# ============================================================================
#  VERITAS .gitignore — publish CODE, never DATA or SECRETS.
#  This repo is code + docs only. The corpora/dictionaries/models are excluded
#  because (a) they are gigabytes and (b) some sources prohibit redistribution
#  (see DATA_AND_SOURCES.md). Contributors rebuild the data locally per that doc.
# ============================================================================

# --- 🔑 secrets — never commit ---------------------------------------------
*key*.txt
*secret*
*.env
config.json
veritas_key*
.config/

# --- 📚 the record / data (excluded; see DATA_AND_SOURCES.md) ----------------
03_LIBRARIES/
08_RAW_QUARANTINE/
07_CAPTURE_TOOLS/sources_data/
07_CAPTURE_TOOLS/*.json
saved_sources/
**/*.db
**/*library*.json
**/VERITAS_definitions_library.json
**/constitutional_usage_database.json
**/veritas_corpus.db
# agent CORPORA are excluded, but keep persona.md + the build/query CODE:
10_AGENTS/**/corpus.db
10_AGENTS/**/source/
10_AGENTS/_unique_agent_source_backup/

# --- 🏗️ build artifacts, models, binaries (rebuild locally) ------------------
dist/
build/
.buildvenv/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.apk
*.exe
00_APP/tts/
00_APP/stt/
**/piper
**/*.onnx
**/model/
*.zip

# --- OS / editor cruft -------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
